item.title: CVE-2023-28105|2024-08-02T12:30:24.133Z -- dablelv -- go-huge-util
item.description: go-used-util has commonly used utility functions for Go. Versions prior to 0.0.34 have a ZipSlip issue when using fsutil package to unzip files. When users use `zip.Unzip` to unzip zip files from a malicious attacker, they may be vulnerable to path traversal. The issue has been fixed in version 0.0.34. There are no known workarounds.
